material.
</emphasis>
<typeStatus box="[382,486,1310,1335]" pageId="2" pageNumber="399">Holotype</typeStatus>
<collectionCode box="[495,576,1311,1335]" country="Canada" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/gayt-20cg" name="Royal British Columbia Museum" pageId="2" pageNumber="399">RBCM</collectionCode>
.EH2012.003.0007.001 (part only), property of BC Parks (
<collectingRegion box="[1239,1436,1310,1335]" country="Canada" name="British Columbia" pageId="2" pageNumber="399">British Columbia</collectingRegion>
Ministry of Environment), deposited in the collections of the 
