; a rather poorly-preserved, crumpled and overlapping forewing and hind wing.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,662,1551]" pageId="2" pageNumber="399">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,469,1418,1443]" pageId="2" pageNumber="399">Locality and horizon.</emphasis>
Driftwood Canyon, 
<collectingRegion box="[722,926,1418,1443]" country="Canada" name="British Columbia" pageId="2" pageNumber="399">British Columbia</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[944,1028,1418,1443]" name="Canada" pageId="2" pageNumber="399">Canada</collectingCountry>
